                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Infra + COGS</td>
                        <td>~$15K</td>
                        <td>~$130K</td>
                        <td>~$500K</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Total opex</td>
                        <td>~$165K</td>
                        <td>~$530K</td>
                        <td>~$1.3M</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 8: Bootstrapped + Team -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-label">Team & Traction</div>
        <h2 class="slide-headline">Self-funded.<br>Built from scratch.</h2>
        <div class="slide-body" style="display: flex; gap: 4rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <div>
                <p><strong>What exists today:</strong></p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                    <li style="border: none; padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.5rem;">&middot;&ensp;Working app with local voice transcription + graph-native memory</li>
                    <li style="border: none; padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.5rem;">&middot;&ensp;Multi-platform: phone, Telegram, Discord, Matrix</li>
                    <li style="border: none; padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.5rem;">&middot;&ensp;Functional pendant prototype (on stage today)</li>
                    <li style="border: none; padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.5rem;">&middot;&ensp;Daily beta launching this month &middot; PBC incorporated in Colorado</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><strong>The team:</strong></p>
                <div class="people" style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 2; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                    <em>Aaron Gabriel Neyer</em> &mdash; Founder, product &amp; architecture<br>
                    <em>Jon Bo</em> &mdash; Daily co-lead, founding engineer<br>
                    <em>Lucian Hymer</em> &mdash; Computer co-lead, founding engineer<br>
                    <em>Marvin Melzer</em> &mdash; Hardware, pendant prototype<br>
                    <em>Neil Yarnal</em> &mdash; Brand &amp; design
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--fg-dim); margin-top: 2rem;">MA Ecopsychology &middot; MS Creative Technology & Design (CU ATLAS) &middot; Founding engineer &times;2 &middot; Ex-Google &middot; 10+ years full stack</p>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 9: The Ask -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-label">The Ask</div>
        <h2 class="slide-headline">Raising $300K to hire<br>the core team.</h2>
        <div class="ask-box">
            <div class="ask-row"><span class="lbl">Instrument</span><span class="val">SAFE (YC standard)</span></div>
            <div class="ask-row"><span class="lbl">Use of funds</span><span class="val">Core team full-time through 2026</span></div>
            <div class="ask-row"><span class="lbl">Goal</span><span class="val">Production launch by June &middot; revenue immediately</span></div>
